  "title": "Legal Counsel",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job ID: [1419155]</strong></p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Draft, review, and negotiate contracts, agreements, and other legal documents.</li><li>Provide legal advice and support on a wide range of commercial issues.</li><li>Manage the establishment and closure of subsidiaries, associates, branches, and project offices.</li><li>Coordinate with external legal counsels and monitor the progress of their work.</li><li>Advise and collaborate with business units and departments on legal matters.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>Candidate must possess a Degree in law.</li><li>Minimum 4 years of post-qualification experience, preferably with knowledge of construction law or experience in the construction industry.</li><li>Strong analytical and problem-solving abilities; proactive and independent.</li><li>Ability to work both independently and collaboratively within a team.</li><li>High attention to detail and capability to manage multiple tasks effectively.</li><li>Open to travel when required.</li></ul><p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be notified. However, rest assured that all applications will be updated to our resume bank for future opportunities.</p><p>Please kindly refer to the Privacy Policy of Good Job Creations for your reference: https://goodjobcreations.com.sg/en/privacy-policy/</p><p>EA Personnel Name: Felicia Chiam Kar Min<br />EA Personnel Reg. No.: R25152370<br />EA Licence No.: 07C5771 </p>",
